entries.journal_entry_description: Apprehend a suspected Force-sensitive Twi'lek hiding on Endor and find the Rebels who have been aiding him.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Apprehend a suspected Force-sensitive Twi'lek hiding on Endor. His name is Zalbar Jyvun. His camp is believed to be near the Marauder's Stronghold on Endor.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: As suspected, some Rebels have been hiding Zalbar. But we now know where to find them. Go to Lok and eliminate them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Loam Redge: "As suspected, some Rebels have been hiding Zalbar. But we now know where to find them. Go eliminate them."
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Go to the base camp of the Rebels on Lok who were helping the Twi'lek and destroy it. We know the camp's general area, but you may have to search for it.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Loam Redge at the Emperor's Retreat.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Rebel commander, Captain Jeza Goloc.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Destroy their supply caches at the camp.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Search Zalbar Jyvun's Camp for information on whoever is helping him hide.
